    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers practical transportation for a budget-conscious buyer. The exterior shows visible signs of its age, including several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the trim pieces. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows clear signs of wear and some staining from regular use. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, though it lacks the smoothness of a newer model and may require some minor maintenance in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has served its previous owner well and is priced to reflect its current state.",
