    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-quality masterpiece that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and it shows in every detail. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, and has been treated with a high-end ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple without a single crease or sign of bolster wear, and the dashboard is pristine with no sun fading. Every electronic component, from the navigation system to the ambient lighting, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. With a full service history, two sets of keys, and the original window sticker included, this car offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
